    "title": "Lipa Waste Collection Calendar",
    "content": {
      "type": "doc",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "I built this application for a municipal office to make waste collection schedules easier for residents to understand than the original spreadsheet-based format.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "The product centers on practical clarity: a hero section showing the nearest pickup, plus day, week, and month calendar views that make upcoming communal and sorted waste collection dates easy to scan on desktop and mobile.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Under the hood, the project uses a local XLSX-to-JSON parser so the yearly schedule can be refreshed with a low-risk workflow and deployed as a static Next.js application without adding unnecessary operational complexity.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
